    "title": "Principal Fleet Manager at Aramex India South Asia Partners",
    "description": "Aramex India South Asia Partners, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Fleet Manager for our Raipur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Aramex India South Asia Partners:\nAramex India South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Aramex India South Asia Partners!",
